data.title: Weber iGrill 3 - Overview
data.description:
Weber iGrill 3 Bluetooth Thermometer - 7204

Become a backyard genius. No training necessary. Each Weber® Genesis® II and Genesis® LX grill is iGrill 3 ready. The iGrill 3 Bluetooth® thermometer monitors food from beginning to end, and notifies you via the Weber iGrill App once it has reached the perfect degree to serve. Once connected, the possibilities are virtually endless, and you'll find out that the iGrill 3 is more than a cutting-edge thermometer.

Features:

Compatible with Weber Genesis II and Weber Genesis II LX

Weather Resistant

Individual temperature selection

Magnetic attachment

Four Probe Capacity - Includes two Pro Meat Probes

150' Line of Sight Bluetooth® Smart Connection

250 Hour Battery Life

Knob Light Control, exclusively for Genesis II LX

Fuel Level Detection (select models only)

Connect Multiple At Once

Measures -58°F to 716°F or -50°C to 300°C

Weber iGrill App Min/Max Temperature Alarms

Preset and Custom Alarms

Timer

Graphing

Supports Multiple iGrill or Kitchen Thermometer Devices Simultaneously

Social Sharing







In The Box:

iGrill 3

1 Battery Pack Assembly

3 AA Batteries

2 Pro Meat Probes

2 Probe Wraps

2 Colored Probe Indicators

1 Magnetic Fuel Level Sensor Assembly

Installation and Quick Start Guide

data.title: Weber iGrill Mini - Overview
data.description:
Weber iGrill Mini Bluetooth Thermometer, Model 7202

Upgrade your grill and take the guesswork out of grilling! The iGrill Mini is a single probe, wireless Bluetooth® Smart thermometer to tell you when your food has reached your desired temperature.

Includes everything you love about the iGrill with a ton of cool new features packed, into a rugged, pocket-sized design. The iGrill Mini connects using Bluetooth® Smart technology and features a Smart LED, proximity sensor, extended battery life of 150 hours and magnetic mounting. The Weber iGrill app is available for free in the App Store and Google Play Store.

Features:

Single Probe

Bluetooth Smart Connection

Extended Battery Life

Smart LED

Proximity Wake-Up

Connect Multiple At Once

Convenient Mounting

Measures -58°F to 716°F or -50°C to 300°C

Brand New App

Weber iGrill App
Min/Max Temperature Alarms

Preset and Custom Alarms

Timer

Graphing

Supports Multiple iGrill or Kitchen Thermometer Devices Simultaneously

Exclusive Recipes

Social Sharing

data.title: Weber iGrill 2 - Overview
data.description:
Weber iGrill 2 LED Display Thermometer, Model 7203

Designed for the pros, built for everyone! Add this advanced Bluetooth® Smart grilling thermometer to your toolset, complete with professional grade probes, for award-worthy meat.

Grill with precision. A Bluetooth® Smart connected grilling thermometer that allows you to monitor up to four temperatures right from the free Weber® iGrill® app available in the App Store℠ and Google Play™ Store. This is for the serious griller or smoker with four probe ports, two high temp probes, an illuminated display, magnetic mounting and up to 200 hours of battery life.

Features:

Four Probe Capacity - Includes two Pro Meat Probes

150' Line of Sight Bluetooth® Smart Connection

200 Hour Battery Life

Illuminated Display

Proximity Wake-Up

Connect Multiple At Once
